title: Episode 40: One Flew Over the Cukoo's Nest
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: A poet, a sociologist, and a psychologist walk into a... podcast studio to talk about the movie, book, and play "One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest."  Drs. Chuck Rybak, Andrew Austin, and Ryan Martin discuss prominent themes, what it tells us about mental illness, rebellion, connections to nature, and answer listener questions.
